218
00:11:28,681 --> 00:11:33,072
It's not argument. I've had
an accident and I want compensation.

219
00:11:33,161 --> 00:11:37,120
It's not up to me. I've got nothing
to compensate you with.

220
00:11:37,201 --> 00:11:39,556
