407
00:21:58,321 --> 00:22:01,836
(Woman) There's a caff down the road
and they have a striptease.

408
00:22:01,921 --> 00:22:05,277
Every night there's kids hanging
round to get in and see 'em.

409
00:22:05,361 --> 00:22:07,829
It puts ideas in the kids' heads.

410
00:22:07,921 --> 00:22:11,630
Stephen, what are you doing?
I told you not to play with the dirt.

411
00:22:11,721 --> 00:22:13,677
Look at your clean jeans.

412
00:22:13,761 --> 00:22:17,390
Put that down. And you, Sean.
Look at you, you're filthy.

413
00:22:17,481 --> 00:22:19,597
(Cathy) Now I was pregnant again.

414
00:22:19,681 --> 00:22:23,117
Some say it's wrong to have another
kiddie when you're overcrowded.

415
00:22:23,201 --> 00:22:25,157
But I don't think so.

416
00:22:25,241 --> 00:22:27,232
I think kiddies are God's gift.

417
00:22:27,321 --> 00:22:30,870
You do wrong to deprive anyone
of the chance of life.

418
00:22:30,961 --> 00:22:32,952
Love's what's important
in a child's life.

419
00:22:33,041 --> 00:22:36,033
Love is more important
than nice surroundings.

420
00:22:36,121 --> 00:22:39,158
I know, cos I lived
in a "respectable" home.

421
00:22:39,241 --> 00:22:41,277
And I didn't have it.

422
00:22:41,361 --> 00:22:44,990
(Woman) We have to sleep in
the attic, like, and it's quite damp.

423
00:22:45,081 --> 00:22:48,312
He wallpapered it about three weeks
before I had the baby,

424
00:22:48,401 --> 00:22:52,189
and the far wall is starting
to come down already.

425
00:22:52,281 --> 00:22:55,000
- Help!
- Mrs Alley, are you all right?

426
00:22:55,081 --> 00:22:58,278
I fell through the bed!
Thank you, ducks, thank you.

427
00:22:58,361 --> 00:23:00,317
I'm very grateful to you, ducks.

428
00:23:00,401 --> 00:23:04,076
Mrs Alley, I can't pull any harder,
I'll lose the baby!

429
00:23:04,161 --> 00:23:06,117
Aren't I a silly girl?

430
00:23:06,841 --> 00:23:08,832
Pull me, harder!

431
00:23:08,921 --> 00:23:11,151
Oh, I wets the bed, see?

432
00:23:11,681 --> 00:23:14,878
I wets the bed
